title: [P3D] Prepar3d 3.2 Patches only
description:
P3D V3.2 patches


If you don't want to do a full re-install, this is the client updates only for pro, pro+ and academic with cracks included.


Follow the instructions in the readme.


and FYI Orbx have not released an update for this new version yet, so if it crashes due to object_flow don't blame me.
